 results for 24 and 70 microns provide strong consistent\nevidence for the universality of the mid-IR/radio and far-IR/radio correlations\nout to redshifts of at least z = 1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2004 18:50:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
