wed disks\nshould display weaker PAH emission than flared disks, consistent with our\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2004 07:26:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2004 14:08:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Aug 2004 13:39:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
